reviewText: Shake yo butt good.. Bahamian fingerpickin bliss....what u have hesitation fever....FU....this stuff heals everything!
mr wald has a big grin on his face for the whole time.
If you like the music of Joseph Spence and want to learn his unique style of playing, this DVD set of lessons by Elijah Wald is absolutely superb. Worth every penny.

Elijah Wald captures Joseph Spence's playing as close to the real thing as you can get. He has a real respect for the man and the music, which comes through in his playing and teaching. An excellent video!
